pageContext.description: Loop  broken right off. Slight traces of light coloured earth.
pageContext.patina: One side medium green patina and on the other light blue.

pageContext.associations: Part of a hoard consisting of 9 s. celts, a spear head, 2 gouges, portion of knife, etc. A socketed celt and an equal weight of rough ore now in the Museum of the Royal Academy of Literature, History, and Antiquities, Stockholm.
